comment: Chalmers (MEM) makes body to body contact with Jennings (DET) that affects his RSBQ.
Allen (MEM) grabs Drummond (DET) after he secures the rebound.
Jennings (DET) makes contact with Chalmers' (MEM) arm and affects his shot attempt.
RHH shows Barnes (MEM) makes contact with Morris' (DET) off-arm that prevents him from gathering and causes him to lose possession of the ball.
Baynes' (DET) momentum carries him into Chalmers (MEM) and he makes contact with his legs while he is in the act of shooting.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the free throw hit the rim was confirmed.
